statement.tex:
\text{Find the relationship between a and b so}\\ \text{that the function f defined by}\\
f(x) = \begin{cases} ax + 1, if \,x\leq 3\\ bx + 3, if \,x\gt 3 \\ \end{cases}\\
\text{Is continuous at x=3}

step.reason:
\text{For a function to be continuous at a\\
point it's limits on either sides should be\\
equal to the value of f(x) at that point}
